==Chronology== :{| class="wikitable" |- ! Date ! Flag ! Image |- |1793–1794 |British [[Red Ensign]]<ref name="fotw.net" /> | style="text-align:center;"|[[File:Red Ensign of Great Britain (1707-1800).svg|border|50px]] |- |1794–1816 |[[Flag of Great Britain]] (probably not updated in 1801) | style="text-align:center;"|[[File:Union flag 1606 (Kings Colors).svg|border|50px]] |- |1816–1843 |Early version of the present flag | style="text-align:center;"|[[File:Flag of Hawaii (1816).svg|border|50px]] |- |February 1843 – July 1843 |Union Flag (during the [[Paulet Affair (1843)|Paulet Affair]]) | style="text-align:center;"|[[File:Flag of the United Kingdom.svg|border|50px]] |- |July 1843 – May 1845 |Early version of the present flag | style="text-align:center;"|[[File:Flag of Hawaii (1816).svg|border|50px]] |- |December 1845 – February 1893 |The current Hawaiian flag introduced in 1845 | style="text-align:center;"|[[File:Flag of Hawaii (1896).svg|border|50px]] |- |February 1893 – April 1893 |[[Flag of the United States|U.S. flag]] (after the [[overthrow of the Kingdom of Hawaii]]) | style="text-align:center;"|[[File:Flag of the United States (1891-1896).svg|border|50px]] |- |1894–1898 |Hawaiian flag re-adopted by the [[Republic of Hawaii]] | style="text-align:center;"|[[File:Flag of Hawaii (1896).svg|border|50px]] |- |1898–1959 |Hawaiian flag used by the U.S. [[territory of Hawaii]] | style="text-align:center;"|[[File:Flag of Hawaii.svg|border|50px]] |- |1959–present |Hawaiian flag currently used by the [[State of Hawaii]] | style="text-align:center;"|[[File:Flag of Hawaii.svg|border|50px]] |}
